schedule
Class Schedule

java.lang.Object
  schedule.Schedule

public class Schedule
extends java.lang.Object

Schedule is the main driver of the scheduling process. It handles the loading of various data files and holds the setting for various configs such as generic classrooms/size and scheduling options such as affinity/class distribution.

Author:
Billy Lynch, Jenny Shi
